\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35519,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/04\/03\/prophet-prays-servant\/","url_meta":{"origin":9621,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Funerals: The Prophet prays for a humble mosque servant","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 3, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: A black woman, or a young man, used to maintain the mosque and one day the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, missed her and asked about her. They said, \u201cShe has died.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cYou would not announce it to me?\u201d It\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19386,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/06\/21\/brothers-of-prophet-all-believers\/","url_meta":{"origin":9621,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Companions: The Prophet is the brother of all believers","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 21, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cI wish I could meet my brothers.\u201d The companions of the Prophet said, \u201cAre we not your brothers?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cYou are my companions, but my brothers are those who have faith in me\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37570,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/12\/19\/salah-3-times\/","url_meta":{"origin":9621,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Salat: The Prophet stresses the greatness of prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 19, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: A man came to the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, and he asked him about the best of deeds. The Prophet said, \u201cPrayer.\u201d The man said, \u201cThen what?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cThen prayer.\u201d The man said, \u201cThen what?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cThen\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19348,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/06\/17\/prophet-lightens-salat-for-child\/","url_meta":{"origin":9621,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Ease: The Prophet lightens prayer on occasion","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 17, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, I might\u00a0begin the prayer and I intend to prolong it, but then I hear the crying of an infant. I will\u00a0shorten the prayer as\u00a0I know his crying will distress his mother.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 710, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/9621","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\